    "subtitle": "Daily historical price and volume data for 10 top cryptocurrencies (market_cap)",
    "description": "This dataset provides daily historical data for 10 major cryptocurrencies. Each row represents a single trading day, covering the maximum range that was available at the time of extraction.\n\nKey Features\n\nClosing Price and Volume: For each cryptocurrency, two columns are provided:\n\nxxx_closing_price – The daily closing price in USD\n\nxxx_volume – The daily trading volume\n\nDate Format: Each date is listed in “dd/mm/yy” format for easy reading.\n\nTop 10 Cryptocurrencies: Includes well-known coins such as Bitcoin, Ethereum, and others with high market capitalization.\n\n- Potential Uses\n\n1.Exploratory data analysis or visualizations of crypto market trends\n\n2.Time-series modeling, forecasting, or anomaly detection\n\n3.Comparative studies between multiple cryptocurrencies\n\n=== About this file ===\n\nAbout this file\nThis CSV contains daily historical data for 10 popular cryptocurrencies, with columns for each coin’s closing price and trading volume (e.g., btc_closing_price, btc_volume). Dates are formatted in dd/mm/yy, and tickers (e.g., BTC-USD) identify which cryptocurrency pair the data belongs to.\n\n\n=== Columns & descriptions ===\n\nDate: Curriencies price\nbtc_closing_price: Daily closing price of Bitcoin (BTC) in USD.\nbtc_volume: Daily trading volume of Bitcoin.\neth_closing_price: Daily closing price of Ethereum (ETH) in USD.\neth_volume: Daily trading volume of Ethereum\nusdt_closing_price: Daily closing price of Tether (USDT) in USD.\nusdt_volume: Daily trading volume of Tether.\nxrp_closing_price: Daily closing price of XRP in USD.\nxrp_volume: Daily trading volume of XRP.\nbnb_closing_price: Daily closing price of BNB (Binance Coin) in USD.\nbnb_volume: Daily trading volume of BNB.\nsol_closing_price: Daily closing price of Solana (SOL) in USD\nsol_volume: Daily trading volume of Solana.\nusdc_closing_price: Daily closing price of USDC\nusdc_volume: Daily trading volume of USDC\ndoge_closing_price: Daily closing price of Dogecoin (DOGE) in USD.\ndoge_volume: Daily trading volume of Dogecoin.\nada_closing_price: Daily closing price of Cardano (ADA) in USD.\nada_volume: Daily trading volume of Cardano.\ntrx_closing_price: Daily closing price of TRON (TRX) in USD.\ntrx_volume: Daily trading volume of TRON.\n",
